3 LIMPIEZA DE DATOS

#Limpio los datos de las columnas quitando los espacios y cambiandolos por guiones, puesto que los espacios dan bastantes problemas a la hora de llamar a las variables
names(laliga) <- gsub(" ","_", names(laliga))
# Limpieza de variables que no nos interesan
laliga$Score <-  NULL
laliga$`Half_Time_Score` <- NULL
laliga$`Match_Excitement` <- NULL
laliga$`Home_Team_Rating` <- NULL
laliga$`Away_Team_Rating` <- NULL
laliga$`Home_Team_Goals_Conceeded` <- NULL
laliga$`Away_Team_Goals_Conceeded` <- NULL
# Aadimos la columna resultado (tipo quiniela)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, resultado = ifelse(Home_Team_Goals_Scored-Away_Team_Goals_Scored > 0, "1",
                                          ifelse(Home_Team_Goals_Scored-Away_Team_Goals_Scored < 0, "2", "x")))

# Aadimos la columna con los goles, tiros, tiros bloqueados, corners, centros, duelos aereos ganados, despejes, faltas, amarillas y rojas totales (por partido)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, goles = Home_Team_Goals_Scored + Away_Team_Goals_Scored)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_disparos = laliga$Home_Team_Total_Shots + laliga$Away_Team_Total_Shots)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_disparos_bloqueados = laliga$Home_Team_Blocked_Shots + laliga$Away_Team_Blocked_Shots)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_corners = laliga$Home_Team_Corners + laliga$Away_Team_Corners)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_centros = laliga$Home_Team_Throw_Ins + laliga$Away_Team_Throw_Ins)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_d_aereos = laliga$Home_Team_Aerials_Won + laliga$Away_Team_Aerials_Won)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_despejes = laliga$Home_Team_Clearances + laliga$Away_Team_Clearances)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_faltas = laliga$Home_Team_Fouls + laliga$Away_Team_Fouls)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_amarillas = laliga$Home_Team_Yellow_Cards + laliga$Away_Team_Yellow_Cards)
laliga <- mutate(laliga, total_rojas = laliga$Home_Team_Red_Cards + laliga$Away_Team_Red_Cards)


#Aadimos las columnas Home points y Away points
laliga <- mutate(laliga, Home_points = case_when(laliga$resultado == 1 ~ 3,
                                                 laliga$resultado == "x" ~ 1,
                                                 laliga$resultado == 2 ~ 0))
laliga <- mutate(laliga, Away_points = case_when(laliga$resultado == 1 ~ 0,
                                                 laliga$resultado == "x" ~ 1,
                                                 laliga$resultado == 2 ~ 3))
#aadimos una columna con la jornada
laliga <- mutate(laliga, jornada = ceiling(row_number() / 10)) %>%
        mutate(jornada = (jornada - 1) %% 38 + 1)
# Convertimos a categorias
laliga$Home_Team <- as.factor(laliga$Home_Team)
laliga$Away_Team <- as.factor(laliga$Away_Team)
laliga$resultado <- as.factor(laliga$resultado)




# Dividimos los datos en dos datasets (train y test)
test <- filter(laliga, year==2020)
train <- filter(laliga, year<2020)
#write.csv(test,"test/test_laliga.csv")
#write.csv(train,"train/train_laliga.csv")
# dataframes separados por resultado
Victorias_casa <- train %>% filter(resultado==1)
Derrotas_casa <- train %>% filter(resultado==2)
Empates <- train %>% filter(resultado=="x")
